{"title":"青马大桥","authors":["喻大翔"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":6,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"青马大桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喻大翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九九七年五月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青马大桥通车，被港人自豪地称为“香港的新标志”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看相思树在想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听紫荆花在笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金风玉露降青马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山海海起大桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银色长虹飞渡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天河不再迢迢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百五十五年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水流离了大陆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五万六千余天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海峡隔绝了海岛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船的梦想载浮载沉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台风之手亦摇亦飘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李商隐的别离唱了又唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秦观的暗恨如水滔滔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过伶仃洋的诗人仍在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩叹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水淼淼城遥遥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，龙鼓早擂动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平洲卷红潮（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高天的理想画在大屿山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回归的足音响遍赤?角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古今岁月读香江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青马诸岛架鹊桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天七月七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也无暮与朝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披两岸的绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映一海的蓝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流泻的银辉更俊俏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光日夜奏琴弦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比乐圣的旋律更美妙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太平山下现代曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青马乐团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让五洲四海起波涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，欢庆的人群在涌流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪在奔跑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑过香江桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑过罗湖桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑过赵州桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年万里连一线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是祖国把手招"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）龙鼓洲为香港最西部小岛；平洲为香港最东部小岛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：海南师范大学）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}